KitKat::

She made it to the entrance and was about to collapse. She rested 
against the wall next to the main entrance and searched for the 
strength to get up.  She hauled herself up and went out the entrance. 
She stopped at the small closet compartment just on the inside of the 
doorway and grabbed an emergency ration of energon.  She tucked it in 
her shoulder compartment and went back to the battle grounds. 

It took her a while, but she finally made it. Her internal life meter 
was showing her power levels at 40%.  She groaned and continued on. 
She made her way to the battle field. She stopped as she found the 
scent of Windlord. She smelled the air. Even in bot mode, her sences 
of hearing and smell were still very keen.  She followed the smell. 
She could also smell three other bots with that one. She did not know 
what she would find, but she would be willing to take it on. She drew 
her pistol and followed her nose.
